Class PSWsHelperFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.integration.PSWsHelperFactory

public class PSWsHelperFactory
extends Object

This factory class holds the appropriate class to instantiate instance of the interface IPSWsHelper. Examples of using this class can be found in the tag library source included with Rhythmyx. See the file taglibsrc.jar
